Text: Thanks so much for this u/l.  I have the previous u/l by KK but when I read "The Lovers", it only had the first 20 chapters in it.  I couldn't find it anywhere else.  Needless to say, I checked your posted book and it is complete, as all your posted books are.  Now I can finally find out how the book ends.  Thanks for all your u/l's.  CP
